!!!PARs New correlation, FR-1500 (named "a") FR-960 20 Units each.  1500 type in both annulus (4 in total), 10 in DOME and 2 in each SG. 960 type 2 in CAVITY, 4 in each SG, 3 in PZR, 1 in each stairs (2 in total), 1 in OP
!!!!Next records are for FR90/1-960 in cavity. There are 2 of them!!!
!
!			cfname			icfnum		cftype
